@startuml seq-04-article-by-category
' 序列图4：按分类查文章
title 按分类查文章序列图

actor 用户 as User
participant "index.js" as Front
participant "ArticleController" as Ctrl
participant "ArticleService" as Svc
participant "ArticleMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB

User -> Front: 点击分类tab(结构/家具/木料/工具/教程)
Front -> Ctrl: GET /api/article/category/{cid}
Ctrl -> Svc: byCategory(cid)
Svc -> Mapper: selectByCategory(cid)
Mapper -> DB: SELECT * FROM article WHERE category_id=?
DB --> Mapper: List<Article>
Mapper --> Svc: List<Article>
Svc --> Ctrl: List<Article>
Ctrl --> Front: {code:200, data:List}
Front -> Front: _fixUrl()拼接baseUrl
Front --> User: 切换显示该分类文章

@enduml
